SYNOPSIS

* Place all contents of this directory (and subdirectories) in /home/ubuntu on
  a new EC2 Ubuntu Server instance.
* run bootstrap_ec2.sh
* edit params.sh
* run setup_mifos.sh
* make sure any/all changes make it back into source control

CONTENTS

* bootstrap_ec2.sh *
first script to run to provision an Ubuntu server EC2 instance destined to host
Mifos instances

* setup_mifos.sh *
spin up a new Mifos instance

* lib.sh *
functions and data for the above

* params.sh *
data for setup_mifos.sh

* templates/ *
parameterized config files

* contrib *
Other scripts. For instance, a Makefile for remote backups of these
provisioning scripts
